sequenceDiagram
    actor Analyst as 👤 Analyst
    participant DD as 🐛 DefectDojo UI
    participant APIM as 🔷 APIM
    participant CA as 📦 Container App
    participant SRCH as 🔍 Azure AI Search
    participant AOAI as 🤖 Azure OpenAI
    participant MCP as 🛠️ MCP Server
    participant ADO as 📁 Azure DevOps
    participant DDAPI as 🐛 DefectDojo API

    rect rgb(220, 235, 255)
        Note over Analyst,DDAPI: ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━  DETECT-SECRETS FLOW  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    end

    Analyst->>DD: 1. Click AI Triage
    DD->>APIM: POST /triage/batch
    APIM->>CA: Forward request
    CA-->>DD: Return jobId

    rect rgb(255, 245, 220)
        Note over CA,SRCH: STEP 2 — RAG fires BEFORE model sees anything
        CA->>SRCH: Hybrid search (vector + keyword)
        Note right of CA: query = "hardcoded credential<br/>secret {rule_name} CWE-798"
        SRCH-->>CA: Top 3 docs returned:
        Note right of SRCH: [CWE-798] Hard-coded Credentials<br/>[OWASP A02:2021] Cryptographic Failures<br/>[MITRE T1552] Unsecured Credentials
    end

    rect rgb(235, 255, 235)
        Note over CA,AOAI: STEP 3 — RAG context injected into prompt
        CA->>AOAI: Send prompt WITH RAG context
        Note right of CA: === AUTHORITATIVE SECURITY KNOWLEDGE ===<br/>[CWE-798] definition + mitigations<br/>[OWASP A02] context<br/>[MITRE T1552] attack pattern<br/>=== END SECURITY KNOWLEDGE ===<br/>+ finding metadata
    end

    rect rgb(245, 235, 255)
        Note over AOAI,ADO: STEP 4 — Model calls fetch_code tool
        AOAI->>CA: tool_use: fetch_code {file_path, line_number}
        CA->>ADO: GET file via ADO REST API
        ADO-->>CA: Code snippet (secret value REDACTED)
        CA->>AOAI: tool_result: code context
    end

    rect rgb(235, 255, 245)
        Note over AOAI,CA: STEP 5 — Model classifies with full context
        AOAI-->>CA: Final JSON response
        Note right of AOAI: classification: true_positive / false_positive / needs_review<br/>confidence: 0.0 - 1.0<br/>reasoning: anchored to RAG knowledge<br/>mitigation: from CWE-798 knowledge base<br/>cwe_reference: CWE-798<br/>references: OWASP mapping
    end

    rect rgb(255, 235, 235)
        Note over CA,DDAPI: STEP 6 — Policy Engine + Write-back
        CA->>CA: Policy Engine validate (confidence ≥ 0.7?)
        CA->>DDAPI: PATCH finding — tags + mitigation + references
        CA->>DDAPI: POST note — full AI triage result + timestamp
        alt confidence < 0.7 OR needs_review
            CA->>DDAPI: Add tag ANALYST_REVIEW_NEEDED
            Note over DD: Review button appears on finding
        end
    end

    rect rgb(220, 235, 255)
        Note over Analyst,DDAPI: ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━  SAST FLOW (Semgrep / CodeQL / Bandit)  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    end

    Analyst->>DD: 1. Click AI Triage
    DD->>APIM: POST /triage/batch
    APIM->>CA: Forward request
    CA-->>DD: Return jobId

    rect rgb(255, 245, 220)
        Note over CA,SRCH: STEP 2 — RAG fires BEFORE model sees anything
        CA->>SRCH: Hybrid search (vector + keyword)
        Note right of CA: query = "{rule_name} SAST<br/>vulnerability {severity}"
        SRCH-->>CA: Top 3 docs returned
        Note right of SRCH: e.g. SQL injection finding:<br/>[CWE-89] SQL Injection<br/>[OWASP A03:2021] Injection<br/>[MITRE T1190] Exploit Public-Facing App
    end

    rect rgb(235, 255, 235)
        Note over CA,AOAI: STEP 3 — RAG context injected into prompt
        CA->>AOAI: Send prompt WITH RAG context
        Note right of CA: === AUTHORITATIVE SECURITY KNOWLEDGE ===<br/>[CWE-89] definition + mitigations<br/>[OWASP A03] injection context<br/>[MITRE T1190] attack pattern<br/>=== END SECURITY KNOWLEDGE ===<br/>+ finding metadata
    end

    rect rgb(245, 235, 255)
        Note over AOAI,DDAPI: STEP 4 — Model calls MCP tools in sequence
        AOAI->>CA: tool_use: fetch_finding {finding_id}
        CA->>MCP: POST /tools/fetch_finding
        MCP->>DDAPI: GET finding — CWE, severity, description
        DDAPI-->>MCP: Full finding data
        MCP-->>CA: Finding context
        CA->>AOAI: tool_result: finding data

        AOAI->>CA: tool_use: fetch_code {file_path, line_number}
        CA->>MCP: POST /tools/fetch_code
        MCP->>ADO: GET file + context lines
        ADO-->>MCP: Code snippet
        MCP-->>CA: Code context
        CA->>AOAI: tool_result: code snippet

        Note over AOAI: Optional — if sanitizer referenced
        AOAI->>CA: tool_use: fetch_related_file {file_path}
        CA->>MCP: POST /tools/fetch_related_file
        MCP->>ADO: GET related file
        ADO-->>MCP: File content
        MCP-->>CA: File content
        CA->>AOAI: tool_result: related file
    end

    rect rgb(235, 255, 245)
        Note over AOAI,CA: STEP 5 — Model classifies with full context
        AOAI-->>CA: Final JSON response
        Note right of AOAI: classification: true_positive / false_positive / needs_review<br/>confidence: 0.0 - 1.0<br/>reasoning: anchored to RAG + code evidence<br/>mitigation: from CWE knowledge base + code-specific fix<br/>cwe_reference: precise CWE mapping<br/>references: OWASP + Semgrep rule link
    end

    rect rgb(255, 235, 235)
        Note over CA,DDAPI: STEP 6 — Policy Engine + Write-back
        CA->>CA: Policy Engine validate (confidence ≥ 0.7?)
        CA->>DDAPI: PATCH finding — tags + mitigation + references
        CA->>DDAPI: POST note — full AI triage result + timestamp
        alt confidence < 0.7 OR needs_review
            CA->>DDAPI: Add tag ANALYST_REVIEW_NEEDED
            Note over DD: Review button appears on finding
        end
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
        Note over Analyst,DDAPI: ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━  KEY DIFFERENCE RAG MAKES  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
        Note over CA,AOAI: WITHOUT RAG: model relies on training memory → inconsistent CWE mapping, generic mitigations, confidence varies
        Note over CA,SRCH: WITH RAG: authoritative definitions injected at query time → precise CWE/OWASP/MITRE mapping, specific mitigations, consistent results
    end
